    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for anyone looking for a functional car at an affordable price. The engine and transmission are in working order, though you may notice some minor mechanical quirks and cosmetic wear consistent with its age and mileage. It has been maintained enough to stay on the road, but it is not in showroom condition. Expect some scratches, interior fading, and the need for minor upkeep in the near future. It\u2019s an honest, dependable car that gets the job done without any frills.",
      "price": 23000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
